rm="translate(74.45 621.73)" class="cls-11"><tspan _ngcontent-ng-c2702153162="" x="0" y="0">Internet Connection</tspan></text></g><g _ngcontent-ng-c2702153162=""><line _ngcontent-ng-c2702153162="" x1="59.7" y1="580.07" x2="59.7" y2="597.52" class="cls-4"></line><text _ngcontent-ng-c2702153162="" transform="translate(74.45 593.36)" class="cls-13"><tspan _ngcontent-ng-c2702153162="" x="0" y="0" class="cls-17">Dedi</tspan><tspan _ngcontent-ng-c2702153162="" x="25.49" y="0" class="cls-25">c</tspan><tspan _ngcontent-ng-c2702153162="" x="31.6" y="0" class="cls-14">ated Connection</tspan></text></g></g></svg></app-platform-map-svg></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></app-lease-web-media-item><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></app-lease-web-media-items-container><!----><!----><!----><!----><app-lease-web-media-items-container _nghost-ng-c491864292="" class="leaseweb-platform-bottom" data-contentful-id="PlatformBottomMediaComponent"><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="leaseweb-platform-bottom undefined"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292=""></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="row"><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="container-fluid container-xl px-4 px-lg-5"><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="row px-3"><app-lease-web-media-item _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 leaseweb-platform-bottom" _nghost-ng-c2431324502=""><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="content-item-list pb-5"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="justify-content-center"><h3 _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="">Netwerk</h3><p _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="lightgrey">Klanten van Leaseweb hebben toegang tot een van 's werelds grootste en meest geavanceerde netwerken. Met 36 Points of Presence en 25 Internet-exchanges over de hele wereld biedt ons netwerk een enorme bandbreedtecapaciteit, superieure snelheden en onovertroffen connectiviteit voor al uw workloads.</p><cx-generic-link _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""><a tabindex="0" class="btn platform-learn-more " title="Meer info" href="nl/why-leaseweb/platform/network"> Meer info <!----></a><!----><!----><!----></cx-generic-link><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></app-lease-web-media-item><app-lease-web-media-item _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 leaseweb-platform-bottom" _nghost-ng-c2431324502=""><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="content-item-list pb-5"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="justify-content-center"><h3 _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="">Datacenters</h3><p _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="lightgrey">We hebben top-tier, ISO-gecertificeerde datacenters op strategische locaties over de hele wereld om de beste toegang tot de belangrijkste zakelijke regio's in Europa, de VS en Azië te garanderen. Elk daarvan is ontworpen volgens de strengste specificaties voor performance, betrouwbaarheid en beveiliging.</p><cx-generic-link _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""><a tabindex="0" class="btn platform-learn-more " title="Meer info" href="nl/why-leaseweb/platform/data-centers"> Meer info <!----></a><!----><!----><!----></cx-generic-link><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></app-lease-web-media-item><app-lease-web-media-item _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 leaseweb-platform-bottom" _nghost-ng-c2431324502=""><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="content-item-list pb-5"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="justify-content-center"><h3 _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="">Automatisering</h3><p _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="lightgrey">Met ons Customer Portal &amp; API hebt u het heft in handen. Omdat het prettig is om controle te hebben, en alles precies zo in te richten als u wilt. We hebben een gebruiksvriendelijk customer portal, en een complete API die u volledige controle geeft. U hebt daarmee een indrukwekkende reeks features om alle aspecten van uw infrastructuur te beheren.</p><cx-generic-link _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""><a tabindex="0" class="btn platform-learn-more " title="Meer info" href="nl/why-leaseweb/platform/automation"> Meer info <!----></a><!----><!----><!----></cx-generic-link><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></app-lease-web-media-item><app-lease-web-media-item _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 leaseweb-platform-bottom" _nghost-ng-c2431324502=""><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="content-item-list pb-5"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="justify-content-center"><h3 _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="">Certificeringen</h3><p _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="lightgrey">Daarom schakelen wij onafhankelijke externe auditors in om te verifiëren dat onze systemen en processen aan de meest recente industrienormen voldoen. Alle relevante certificaten en informatie van de assurancerapporten vindt u hier.</p><cx-generic-link _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""><a tabindex="0" class="btn platform-learn-more " title="Meer info" href="nl/about-us/security-certifications"> Meer info <!----></a><!----><!----><!----></cx-generic-link><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></app-lease-web-media-item><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></app-lease-web-media-items-container><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></cx-page-slot><cx-page-slot position="Section6" class="Section6 has-components"><app-lease-web-media-items-container _nghost-ng-c491864292="" class="knowledge-base" data-contentful-id="KnowledgeBaseMediaComponent"><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="knowledge-base undefined"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292=""></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="row"><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="container-fluid container-xl px-4 px-lg-5"><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="row justify-center"><div _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="homepage-headers col-lg-12 pb-4 mt-4"><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="">Hebt u nog vragen?<br>Onze Knowledge Base is er om u te helpen</h2></div><app-lease-web-media-item _ngcontent-ng-c491864292="" class="col-md-3 col-6 px-1 knowledge-base" _nghost-ng-c2431324502=""><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="col knowledge-base-container content-item-list"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="justify-content-center pt-4"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="image-container pb-4"><cx-generic-link _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502=""><a href="https://kb.leaseweb.com/products" tabindex="0" class="mt-3" title="Producten"><cx-media _ngcontent-ng-c2431324502="" class="is-loading"><img loading="lazy" alt="Leaseweb" title="Leaseweb" src="https://shop-api.leaseweb.com/medias/products.webp?context=bWFzdGVyfGltYWdlc3wxNDYyfGltYWdlL3dlYnB8YURVek